{"word":"G3334 - μετακινέω - metakinéō - met-ak-ee-neh'-o - Move away","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μετακινέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">metakinéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">met-ak-ee-neh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Move away</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அசை"},{"paragraph":"to move from a place, to move away"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3326 - μετά - metá - met-ah'/3326\">G3326</a> and <a href=\"#/G2795 - κινέω - kinéō - kin-eh'-o/2795\">G2795</a>; to <i>stir</i> to a place <i>elsewhere</i>, that is, <i>remove</i> (figuratively): - move away.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2795/2795\">G2795</a>, <a href=\"#/G2796/2796\">G2796</a>, <a href=\"#/G3334/3334\">G3334</a>"}]}